\v 26 ‚ÄúN…ôm…ô suah k…ôti tolkeikei m…ôm…ô otu…ôris…®g lak, in ot…ôkeikei mol i…ôu i…ôk…ôhtul aup…ôn e r…ôhan n…ômi…ôg…ôhi…ôn. In ot…ôkeikei molkeikei p…®k ag…®n i…ôu, mapir…ôk…®s r…ôhan tat…ô m…®ne mam…ô m…®ne r…ôhan p…ôtan m…®ne n…ôt…®n m…®n m…®ne pian m…®n m…®ne n…ôuv…®n…®n m…®n, m…®ne in …ôhruahru m…®n.\f + \fr 14:26  \ft N…ôghati…ôn Kris …ôhruahru t…ôt…ôni m…ôm…ô, i…ôt…ômi tolkeikei m…ôm…ô otu…ôris…®g e Iesu, in ot…ôkeikei m…ôm…ôki e r…ôhan m…®n. M…ôt…ôu n…®p…ôt…® nati u m…ôm…ô, kitah okotolkeikei kitah m…®n, m…ôt…ôu okot…ôkeikei mautolkeikei p…®k ag…®n Iesu.\f* K…ôni n…ôm…ô t…ôsoli…ôn lan…ôha, ko in t…ôs…ôhmeni…ôn m…ôm…ô otuva r…ôhak i…ôt…ômimi.\x - \xo 14:26  \xt Luk 9:23\x*  
