\v 21 ‚ÄúM…ôt…ôu it…®mah i…ômot…ôl…ôhu=p…ôn pau r…ôhat…®mah n…ôt…ôl…®gi…ôn t…ôtat…®g …ôskas…®k lan m…ôm…ô in otos r…ôk…®s it…®mah n…ôt…ôm Isrel e n…ôhlm…® t…®k…®m…®r m…®n r…ôhat…®mah. K…ôni r…ôueiu in nian tatol k…®s…®l lan.\x - \xo 24:21  \xt Luk 19:11; U…ôk 1:6\x*  
